&lt;h3 id="primary-location">Primary Location&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>This step provides a map with radio buttons for the member to select their primary location. Every location listed in the &lt;strong>YMCA Website Services Location Filter Settings&lt;/strong> (see Troubleshooting section below) is listed.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>
