&lt;h2 id="areas-it-should-be-used">Areas it Should Be Used&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Content Area&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Bottom Area&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="how-to-use-membership-calculator">How to Use Membership Calculator&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>From the paragraphs drop-down, add the &lt;em>Membership Calculator&lt;/em>. No additional configuration is necessary on the page.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Docs: Membership Content Type</title><link>/docs/user-documentation/content-types/membership/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/user-documentation/content-types/membership/</guid><description>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="membership-fields">Membership Fields&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="general-information">General Information&lt;/h3>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Title:&lt;/strong> The title of the membership type to be displayed on the first step of the Membership Calculator.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Description:&lt;/strong> A short description to be displayed on the first step of the Membership Calculator.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Image:&lt;/strong> A reusable image field to be displayed on the first step of the Membership Calculator.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>
&lt;a href="/docs/user-documentation/content-types/membership/membership--general-info.png" title="View original image">
&lt;figure class="image-caption">
&lt;img alt="A screenshot with the Membership content title, image, and description." srcset="
