&lt;figcaption> &lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link fa-fw">&lt;/i>&lt;/figcaption>
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="membership-info">Membership Info&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>The Membership Info Paragraph lists detailed membership information per location. Add one &amp;ldquo;Membership Info&amp;rdquo; section for each location that your membership applies to. If a location does not offer a membership type, you can leave it out.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Location:&lt;/strong> A reference to an already-existing
&lt;a href="../branch">Branch&lt;/a>. If the branch does not exist, you&amp;rsquo;ll need to create it first.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Link:&lt;/strong>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>URL:&lt;/strong> The link a member should be taken to to sign up for this membership at this location. See below for tips on finding this URL.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Link Text:&lt;/strong> This field is not used.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Join Fee:&lt;/strong> Dollar value for how much someone has to pay to join.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Monthly Rate:&lt;/strong> Dollar value for the monthly fee of the membership.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>
